cff-version: 1.2.0
title: VaultRun
message: If you use VaultRun, please cite it as below.
type: software
authors:
  - name: "030.dev / VaultRun"
    email: mail@030.dev
repository-code: "https://github.com/nickvd7/vaultrun"
url: "https://vaultrun.dev"
abstract: >-
  VaultRun is a self-hosted secure runtime for AI agents. It provides isolated
  Docker sandboxes, a 53-tool MCP server (stdio and HTTP), Python and Go SDKs,
  and an HMAC-signed audit trail so agents can execute code and call tools
  without a SaaS dependency.
keywords:
  - AI agents
  - MCP
  - Docker
  - sandbox
  - LLM
  - self-hosted
  - code execution
license: Apache-2.0
version: 0.2.1
date-released: "2026-07-15"
